node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Brittany Jeltema on July 14, 2021 tagging @m_jeltema10, and @thebabynurseohio. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and indoor.

node.text:
OMG we just had the best experience. 👶As y’all know, I’ve had quite a bit of anxiety about the unknowns of motherhood! I’m a hands-on learner, so demonstrations and actually DOING something helps me a lot.

We were gifted a Baby Basics Class from a friend at our baby shower, and @thebabynurseohio CAME TO OUR HOUSE and showed us #allthethings!!!! She literally demonstrated everything from swaddling to diaper changing.

And I’m so glad bc neither of us could figure out these damn baby carriers 😂😂. We learned a whole bunch and even though I’m still nervous, I feel a lot more confident.

Thanks @parentteachermode for the sweet gift! We appreciate it.

node.text:
Welcome to my next BIG project!!! I’ll be flipping this classroom, a reception area, 3 co-working spaces, and the director’s office the FIRST WEEK OF AUGUST! Ahhhh. It’s such a big project and I’m so excited!

It’s also my first HIRED project. If you’re new here, you might not know that I donate classroom makeovers as a way to give back to educators! This administration has put their trust in me to help put together their new school building, and I’m truly honored.

I’m not making a profit yet, but to have this opportunity with SJ on the way is literally a dream come true. Thank you @muensterkl ♥️.

#classroommakeover #classroomdesign #classroomdecor #classroomorganization #classroomlibrary #classroomideas #classroomtransformation #classroomflip

node.text:
Classroom Tip: in small spaces, find items that serve multiple purposes! For example, flexible seating that serves as storage, a gate that also serves as a magnetic wall for student practice, or desks with plexiglass on top as student art display.

To learn more teacher tips, register for the Classroom Environment + Design Conference using the link in my bio!

You’ll have immediate, lifetime access to the sessions. Tickets are only for sale until July 21, so be sure to grab them now!

https://thesuperheroteacher.com/classroom-design-environment-conference-2021

📸: @ohwowtina
#classroomtip #classroomdecor #classroomdesign #classroomsetup #classroommakeover #classroomorganization #teachersofinstagram #teachersofig

node.text:
Classroom Decor Tip: use wainscoting frames from Lowe’s (or any home improvement store) and attach wire/string to the back to hang student work with clothespins!

I like to layer the art with square scrapbooking paper that matches the theme/colors of the classroom!

This is an excellent way to utilize all of the space in your classroom!

#classroomdecor #classroommakeover #classroomdesign #classroomtip #classroomsetup #classroomorganization #classroomlibrary #studentwork #classroomtheme #classroomtransformation

node.text:
I am PUMPED to announce that this year’s ✨ Classroom Design + Environment Conference ✨ is officially LIVE and available for enrollment! I’ll be talking all about how to perfect your classroom atmosphere & design.

This conference goes beyond the basics of aesthetically pleasing classroom decor and dives into the importance of creating an environment and atmosphere that is safe, inclusive, and warm for every student who enters the classroom. 

...and it gets even BETTER! A portion of the earnings from the conference will go towards a classroom makeover for one of the attendees. You’ll have an opportunity to put your name in a drawing to win a transformation from all of the presenters at the conference.

If classroom environment and design is your jam OR you’re looking for a way to improve your classroom atmosphere, this conference is designed for YOU. With 24 presenters, 7+ hours of professional development and 24 FREE resources, you’re sure to strengthen your skills in no time.

💫 Tickets are live for 2 weeks only. Get yours now using the link in my bio 💫

https://thesuperheroteacher.com/classroom-design-environment-conference-2021

#classroomdecor #classroomdesign #classroomsetup #classroomorganization #classroomgoals #classroomenvironment #classroomatmosphere #iteachtoo #teachersofinstagram #teachersofig #teachersofinsta

Entering is simple:
